-- Energy Optimisation × India
('energy-optimisation-consulting-india', 'Energy Optimisation Consulting India | Bombay Breed', 'Expert energy optimization consulting for Indian industries. Reduce costs 15-30% through efficiency improvements and renewable integration.', 'Energy Optimisation Consulting in India', 'combined', true, 80, 'c3da7c4d-69ec-4ab8-a65c-a3ee6d902f19', '3cac1df6-093a-485b-9edf-75e569c36baf', 'India''s PAT scheme and rising energy costs make optimization essential. Expert consulting delivers 15-30% cost reduction with 2-4 year payback.', '[{"question": "What government incentives are available?", "answer": "PAT scheme ESCerts, accelerated depreciation, and state renewable incentives."}, {"question": "Which industries benefit most?", "answer": "Cement, steel, chemicals, textiles, and paper with high energy intensity."}]', '{"introduction": "Indian industries face rising energy costs and regulatory pressure under PAT scheme.", "main_content": "## Our Approach\n\n### Energy Audits\nDetailed audits identifying quick wins and strategic investments.\n\n### Implementation Support\nProject management and vendor selection."}', '[{"url": "/reduce-energy-costs-heavy-industry", "title": "Reduce Energy Costs"}]'),

