('decarbonisation-consulting-india', 'Industrial Decarbonisation Consulting India | Bombay Breed', 'Strategic decarbonisation consulting for Indian industries. Net-zero pathways, technology roadmaps, and implementation support.', 'Industrial Decarbonisation Consulting in India', 'combined', true, 80, '8cdc4dc8-bbd6-4c58-a3bd-09b7cc8139d2', '3cac1df6-093a-485b-9edf-75e569c36baf', 'Indian industries must decarbonise for CBAM compliance and domestic carbon market readiness while maintaining competitiveness.', '[{"question": "Is decarbonisation mandatory in India?", "answer": "Voluntary now, but BRSR reporting and upcoming carbon market create strong drivers."}, {"question": "How does CBAM affect Indian exporters?", "answer": "Steel, aluminium, cement exporters to EU face carbon costs from 2026."}]', '{"introduction": "Indian industries face growing pressure from regulations and customer demands.", "main_content": "## Decarbonisation Services\n\n### Net-Zero Roadmaps\nScience-based pathways aligned with 1.5°C.\n\n### Technology Assessment\nEvaluate options from efficiency to hydrogen."}', '[{"url": "/prepare-for-carbon-border-taxes", "title": "Prepare for CBAM"}]'),

