('climate-investment-readiness-india', 'Climate Investment Readiness India | Bombay Breed', 'Prepare Indian companies for climate finance. Green bonds, transition finance, and DFI funding.', 'Climate Investment Readiness in India', 'combined', true, 75, '4a3007bc-d5a8-4e43-acba-640d1dd33e5f', '3cac1df6-093a-485b-9edf-75e569c36baf', 'India needs $10 trillion for net-zero transition. Investment readiness unlocks green bonds, DFI funding, and carbon finance.', '[{"question": "What climate finance is available in India?", "answer": "Green bonds, SIDBI facilities, DFI loans, and carbon credit financing."}, {"question": "What documentation is needed?", "answer": "Transition plans, ESG policies, and bankable project documentation."}]', '{"introduction": "Indian companies can access growing pool of climate capital.", "main_content": "## Readiness Services\n\n### Transition Planning\nCredible net-zero pathways for investors.\n\n### Project Structuring\nBankable documentation for funding."}', '[{"url": "/article-6-consulting-india", "title": "Article 6 Consulting India"}]'),

